description: The 2025 World Series saw the Los Angeles Dodgers and Toronto Blue Jays engage in a grueling 16-inning Game 3, marking the second-longest World Series game ever. description: Tetsuya Yamagami admitted to the murder of former Prime Minister Shinzo Abe, stating "Everything is true" during his trial. author: TOI TECH DESK
description: Google has refuted claims of a massive Gmail data breach, stating that millions of accounts remain secure. description: Kuwait’s Ministry of Health has introduced new regulations for salons and beauty parlours under Decision No. 194/2025, enforcing stricter hygiene and safety standards.
